### 这个 corner case 非常的危险。 exists 提升产生的是一个 semi。但它处于一个 anti join 之下
### 所以，这个 semi info 对应的 condition 不能和主查询的谓词一起推导新谓词
### 要避免： t3.c1 = v.c1, t1.c1 = v.c1 => t1.c1 = t3.c1, 结合 t3.c1 = 0 推出 t1.c1 = 0
EXPLAIN select c1 from t1 where t1.c1 = 1 and 
	not exists (select 1 from t2 where t2.c1 = t1.c1 and
				exists (select 1 from t3 where t3.c1 = 1 and t3.c1 = 0 and t3.c2 = t2.c2));
